name: NSFileVersion
desc: A snapshot of a file at a specific point in time.

items.name: currentVersionOfItem
items.desc: Returns the most recent version object for the file at the specified URL.

items.name: otherVersionsOfItem
items.desc: Returns all versions of the specified file except the current version.

items.name: version
items.desc: Returns the version of the file that has the specified persistent ID.

items.name: temporaryDirectoryURLForNewVersionOfItem
items.desc: Creates and returns a temporary directory to use for saving the contents of the file.

items.name: addOfItem
items.desc: Creates a version of the file at the specified location.

items.name: url
items.desc: The URL identifying the location of the file associated with the file version object.

items.name: localizedName
items.desc: The string containing the user-presentable name of the file version.

items.name: localizedNameOfSavingComputer
items.desc: The user-presentable name of the computer on which the revision was saved.

items.name: modificationDate
items.desc: The modification date of the version.

items.name: persistentIdentifier
items.desc: The identifier for this version of the file.

items.name: isDiscardable
items.desc: A Boolean value that specifies whether the system can delete the associated file at some future time.

items.name: isConflict
items.desc: A Boolean value indicating whether the contents of the version are in conflict with the contents of another version.

items.name: isResolved
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates the version object is not in conflict (true) or is in conflict (false).

items.name: unresolvedConflictVersionsOfItem
items.desc: Returns an array of version objects that are currently in conflict for the specified URL.

items.name: replaceItem
items.desc: Replace the contents of the specified file with the contents of the current versionâ€™s file.

items.name: remove
items.desc: Remove this version object and its associated file from the version store.

items.name: removeOtherVersionsOfItem
items.desc: Removes all versions of a file, except the current one, from the version store.
